{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were all in the same-- and we were all slated to-- to be treated exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was-- and that's the reason why I think that my parents suffered a lot more than I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they really-- for parents to take care of the children is-- is-- is the normal thing, and they just could-- they couldn't perform that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand that now as an adult, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, exactly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came out of the showers and shaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- they left us out there in the dark, in the cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and the fall of-- of the year in that area gets pretty cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For most of the night we're just standing there naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the scene that must have-- if you could-- you can see that, it looked like this-- this-- these-- this constant motion of naked bodies moving.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in this group, but I know that it was pretty cold to be outside, especially outside of the group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I would work my way in to the middle, where it's a little warmer, where the bodies were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if I stood still long enough, it was pretty soon I was outside again, because everybody else was doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were just kind of moving around the whole time we were out there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And eventually, they-- somebody decided to put us in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- and we were-- the barracks must have been as the size of this room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were all stashed in like you do chairs, with one nested into the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I just-- as soon as it got warm in the barracks, I just fell sleep, just dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- when I woke up, everybody else was asleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
